import React,{useState} from 'react' export default function Contact() { const [form, setForm] = useState({ fullname: "", email: "", phone: "", message: "", }); const handleChange = (e) => { setForm({ ...form, [e.target.name]: e.target.value }); }; const handleSubmit = async (e) => { e.preventDefault(); const res = await fetch("http://localhost:5000/api/contact/add", { method: "POST", headers: { "Content-Type": "application/json" }, body: JSON.stringify(form), }); const data = await res.json(); if (data.success) { alert("Message sent successfully"); setForm({ fullname: "", email: "", phone: "", message: "" }); } else { alert("Failed to send message"); } }; return (
